      "deeperQuestionText": "How does the presence of a Circuit Protective Conductor (CPC) enable a protective device to fulfill the goal of ADS?",
      "deeperAnswerGuidance": [
        "The CPC provides a path for fault current to flow",
        "The fault current allows the protective device to detect the error",
        "The protective device trips or breaks the circuit",
        "Without the CPC path the device might not see the fault to disconnect it"
      ],
      "hint": "Think about the relationship between the path the electricity takes and the device that switches it off."
    }
  ]
}

